data.description: One of the few three-bedroom models on the market in this community today.  Great curb appeal, location, and talk about a wonderful, gated community less than a mile from the Villages, priceless.  This 1450 SF home has an additional Florida Room, with glass windows, tile floor and a separate A/C.   Upgrades include knockdown ceilings, solar tube skylight in living and kitchen, and six panel interior doors.  Roof replaced in 2010, and A/C in 2004.  Stainless appliances include a four-drawer refrigerator, ceramic top range and newer washer and dryer which is located in an inside laundry room.   There is a tiled backsplash and lot of cabinet storage in the kitchen.  The glass enclosed Florida room is light and bright perfect for office, second TV room, and cards or craft room.   The community is golf cart friendly with easy access to shopping, doctor, and anywhere you would like to go with your golf cart.   Community center offers all the fun you could want with clubs, fitness, auditorium, crafts, and out sports of all types.  There is an RV/Boat parking area available for rent, and a 100 acre preserve area to hike, bike, cart ride, and walk your dogs.   Fences are welcome for your pet.  This home is ready to move into and just waiting for its new owners to enjoy it.
